Step 1: Preheat oven to425 degrees F (220 degrees FC). Step 2: Melt Becel(R) Buttery Taste margarine in shallow roasting pan in oven about 2 minutes. Stir in vegetables, rosemary and garlic. Step 3: Roast, stirring twice, 50 minutes or until vegetables are golden and crisp. Nutritional Facts Calories (Kcals): 190 % Daily Value Total Fat: 6g Saturated fat: 1g Trans Fat: 0g Polyunsaturates: 1.9g Omega-6: 1.5g Omega-3: 0.4g Monounsaturates: 2.8g 9% 5% Cholesterol:0mg 0% Sodium:95mg 4% Potassium: 821mg 16% Total Carbohydrate: 34g Dietary Fibre: 7g Sugars: 9g 11% 28% Protein: 3g Vitamin A: 170% Vitamin C: 50% Calcium: 6% Iron: 6% Preparation Time: 10 minutes Cook Time: 50 minutes Total Time: 60 minutes http://www.becel.ca/en/becel/HeartHealthyRecipes/Side-Dishes/Garlic-Rosemary-Roasted-Root-Potatoes.aspx